title: Chad Reed's TwoTwo Tour
description:
Chad needed some etnies TwoTwo gear before heading out to Redbud! Happily, we obliged & hand delivered the goods to his Florida Training Facilities and took a full tour while we were there. Check the edit and then check the goods: etni.es/reed-redbud-ready
etnies TwoTwo product is available now at etnies.com & the etnies tent at this weekend's race!
